## Limitations

This report is based on publicly available information and may not capture all the latest developments in corporate sustainability practices. Additionally, the effectiveness of the strategies mentioned can vary significantly depending on the industry and specific company circumstances. Further research and case studies would be beneficial to provide a more detailed analysis of the impact of these initiatives.